codex
The reference `small.numpress.mzpeak` uses Numpress-linear for m/z and Numpress-SLOF for intensities in chunk mode; the C# default only encodes m/z and leaves intensity as a float list. That is a deliberate-looking divergence in code comments, but it is a schema mismatch against the supplied reference.
